a|bc\iff \exists k\in\mathbb Z,\ bc=ka\iff \exists k\in\mathbb Z,\ \frac{b}{(a,b)}c=k\frac{a}{(a,b)}
(\Rightarrow)
\frac{a}{(a,b)}
\frac{b}{(a,b)}
\frac{a}{(a,b)}|c
(\Leftarrow)
\frac{a}{(a,b)}|c\iff\exists k'\in\mathbb Z,\ c=k'\frac{a}{(a,b)}\Rightarrow \frac{b}{(a,b)}c=\underbrace{\frac{b}{(a,b)}k'}_{=k}\frac{a}{(a,b)}
